  20,8,God‚ÄĒthere is no god ňĻworthy of worshipňļ except Him. He has the Most Beautiful Names
  20,9,Has the story of Moses reached you ňĻO Prophetňļ
  20,10,"When he saw a fire, he said to his family, ‚ÄúWait here, ňĻforňļ I have spotted¬†a fire. Perhaps I can bring you a torch from it, or find some guidance at the fire.‚ÄĚ"
