  25,69,"Their punishment will be multiplied on the Day of Judgment, and they will remain in it forever, in disgrace"
  25,70,"As for those who repent, believe, and do good deeds, they are the ones whose evil deeds God will change into good deeds. For God is All-Forgiving, Most Merciful"
  25,71,And whoever repents and does good has truly turned to God properly
  25,72,"ňĻThey areňļ those who do not bear false witness, and when they come across falsehood, they pass ňĻitňļ by with dignity"
