  25,76,staying there forever. What an excellent place to settle and reside
  25,77,"Say, ňĻO Prophet,ňļ ‚ÄúYou ňĻallňļ would not ňĻevenňļ matter to my Lord were it not for your faith ňĻin Himňļ. But now you ňĻdisbelieversňļ have denied ňĻthe truthňļ, so the torment is bound to come.‚ÄĚ"